snippet.title: SOOT Calisto Gameplay
snippet.description:
In this clip Luis plays the first level of SOOT: Calisto.


The music in-game is from the album Monomyth by Scott Buckley, which sounds awesome:
https://www.scottbuckley.com.au/library/album/monomyth/
